OL,3,CStruggling pupils most likely to have
OL,4,Cnegative phone experiences ` study
OL,6,FSecondary pupils who say they are
OL,7,Fstruggling academically at school are
OL,8,Fmore likely to report having more
OL,9,Fnegative experiences on their phones,
OL,10,Fa study has found.
OL,12,FStudents were particularly likely to
OL,13,Fhave encountered content involving
OL,14,Feating disorders, self-harm and
OL,15,Fsuicide, and upsetting messages in
OL,16,Fonline chat groups with other pupils
OL,17,Fif they said they were struggling
OL,18,Fcompared with if they said they were
OL,19,Fthriving or "coasting" at school, the
OL,20,Fresearch by UWE Bristol academics
OL,21,Ffound.
