OL,3,CStruggling pupils most likely to have
OL,4,Cnegative phone experiences ` study
OL,6,FThe study, which surveyed 3,721
OL,7,Fsecondary pupils at six schools in and
OL,8,Faround Bristol, asked students whether
OL,9,Fthey were "thriving", "coasting, or
OL,10,F"struggling" at school.
OL,12,FPupils were most likely to report
OL,13,Fthemselves as coasting (52%). Only 10%
OL,14,Fsaid they were struggling at school.
OL,16,FSenior lecturer at UWE Bristol's
OL,17,FSchool of Education and Childhood and
OL,18,Fstudy author Dr Ben Knight said young
OL,19,Fpeople who are struggling are likely
OL,20,Fto be experiencing several forms of
OL,21,Fstruggle.
