OL,3,CStruggling pupils most likely to have
OL,4,Cnegative phone experiences ` study
OL,6,FThe 1,595 parents that were also
OL,7,Fsurveyed as part of the study
OL,8,Foverestimated problems their children
OL,9,Fwere experiencing around being ignored
OL,10,For left out, receiving nasty messages,
OL,11,Fhaving sleep problems, or having drama
OL,12,Fwith friends, researchers said.
OL,14,FHowever, parents underestimated the
OL,15,Fextent to which their children
OL,16,Freported seeing disturbing and illegal
OL,17,Fcontent, suicide and self harm
OL,18,Fcontent, eating disorder content, and
OL,19,Fbeing contacted by strangers.
