OL,3,CStruggling pupils most likely to have
OL,4,Cnegative phone experiences ` study
OL,6,FDr Paul Redford, study co-author and
OL,7,Fassociate professor, said: "The
OL,8,Foverall picture is that there are much
OL,9,Fmore serious negative things going on
OL,10,Fwith young people and their
OL,11,Fsmartphones than parents are aware of."
OL,13,FDr Knight said the disconnect is
OL,14,Flikely a result of what children are
OL,15,Fand are not sharing with parents.
