OL,6,F"There's a great deal more at stake
OL,7,Ffor the young people than there is for
OL,8,Fthe parents. They could be thinking
OL,9,F'If my parents or teachers were aware
OL,10,Fof the extent to which I'm seeing
OL,11,Fcertain content, then maybe they take
OL,12,Fmy phone away'," he said.
OL,14,FStudents reported they were most
OL,15,Flikely to have negative experiences on
OL,16,Ftheir phones through group chats,
OL,17,Ffollowed by on social media.
