OL,4,Cnegative phone experiences ` study
OL,6,FThe study also surveyed 352 secondary
OL,7,Fschool teachers across the schools,
OL,8,Fand found more than 70% reported
OL,9,Fhaving seen pupils tired thanks to
OL,10,Fphone use.
OL,12,FSeven in 10 also said they had
OL,13,Fwitnessed conflict in school that
OL,14,Fstarted outside school because of
OL,15,Fphones, and 65% said they had
OL,16,Fwitnessed bullying because of phone
OL,17,Fuse.
