OL,3,CStruggling pupils most likely to have
OL,4,Cnegative phone experiences ` study
OL,6,FTeachers and parents surveyed were
OL,7,Fbroadly in favour of stricter rules on
OL,8,Fschool phone use or keeping rules the
OL,9,Fsame, while more than half (58%) of
OL,10,Fstudents said they would like more
OL,11,Fleniency on phone use at schools.
OL,13,FYoung people who said they were
OL,14,Fstruggling were the most likely to say
OL,15,Fthey would like to see more lenient
OL,16,Frules around school phone use.
