OL,6,FA survey by the Children's
OL,7,FCommissioner earlier this year found
OL,8,F90% of secondary schools and 99.8% of
OL,9,Fprimary schools already have policies
OL,10,Fin place to stop the use of phones
OL,11,Fduring the school day.
OL,13,FHowever, the survey found around 10%
OL,14,Fof secondary schools allowed pupils to
OL,15,Fuse their phones at some point during
OL,16,Fthe school day.
