OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Peter Kyle has
OL,7,Fpreviously said children could face a
OL,8,Flimit on using social media apps. Sky
OL,9,Freported a two-hour cap per platform
OL,10,Fis being considered.
OL,12,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,13,Fsupport headteachers to take the
OL,14,Fnecessary steps to prevent disruption,
OL,15,Fbacked by our clear guidance, and have
OL,16,Falso brought in better protections for
OL,17,Fchildren from harmful content through
OL,18,Fthe Online Safety Act.
